&quot;I will destroy maxi-bots!&quot; Rippersnapper takes the first missile 
from Supernova in the armour, he wobbles then the second follows 
up. knocking him down. He shakes his head, stands up, then 
almost immediately hits the deck, as laser fire and more missiles 
whiz over head. &quot;GRRRRRrrrrrr, Maxi-bots, no play fair,&quot; He gets 
up, fires four voice commanded missiles from his twin launchers at 
Supernova.

Razorclaw waits patiently as the Slasys missiles approach him, 
and at the last second, he leaps straight up, transforms into robot 
mode, levels his out his twin concussion blaster, and fires four 
shots from it. He draws his sonic sword. &quot;Predacons, take out the 
jets!&quot;

Rampage is pacing back and forth, as two laser blasts smash into 
his arm armour plating. &quot;Who&#39;s shooting at me?&quot; He roars not 
expecting a reply. Rampge turms immediately to the nearest flying 
thing, Supernova. He feels the rage building, and he lets it come. &quot;I 
will crush you!&quot; he yells at Supernova, as he jumps into flight, 
charging the Jet with his thermo-sword swinging.

Divebomb, leaps into flight, and transforms, He hears Razorclaw, 
and decides to follow Rampage&#39;s lead. &quot;Well why not,&quot; He pulls out 
his particle beam rifle, and fires two aimed blasts at Supernova.


